{"tid":781114,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"想去帛琉.好多問題......","createTime":"2018-08-15T15:39:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-16T05:27:56.000Z","uid":123701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a95331a493a7e4488207f85a2f9e250cd726b4ff","tid":781114,"uid":123701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T15:39:24.000Z","msg":"請問去帛琉預幾多錢(食住玩)?<br />\n帛琉有咩玩?<br />\n預幾多時間plan行程買機票?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97183981e058ce46a4aa3df7c0896338f18123e3","tid":781114,"uid":37220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T15:48:40.000Z","msg":"連登問呢d地方應該無人理<br />\nbtw 幫手push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e454c2839fe91dbdd3e17708bd6082f193e7693c","tid":781114,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T16:00:17.000Z","msg":"好似香港無直航，要飛台灣先然後轉機直達。聽聞無嘢玩，得陽光與海灘。記住要試下生食海芯內藏"},{"pid":"eb2dcf4a0841baa2db2e7c4d0150eee559e5b746","tid":781114,"uid":197125,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"e454c2839fe91dbdd3e17708bd6082f193e7693c","tid":781114,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T16:00:17.000Z","msg":"好似香港無直航，要飛台灣先然後轉機直達。聽聞無嘢玩，得陽光與海灘。記住要試下生食海芯內藏"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T17:23:43.000Z","msg":"你老母就冇嘢玩，人地海洋保育做得好過好多地方，每年又有限制遊客人數，去一去潛水睇下海洋生物乜都抵返晒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"387116389246f95bbbdc2e1e7c91b80d2327cff4","tid":781114,"uid":196006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T17:43:38.000Z","msg":"係潛水天堂，一個好靚既島國每個dive point都好靚，但比較單一發展，我上年去潛水同考AOW洗左近2皮。<br />\n住左7日民宿，食又民宿，洗得非常慳。<br />\n交通極唔方便，每次潛水有接送，出去要人車。"},{"pid":"6d1469b97821ecdcc07f630351878f44ec4d1d9e","tid":781114,"uid":2267,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"eb2dcf4a0841baa2db2e7c4d0150eee559e5b746","tid":781114,"uid":197125,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"e454c2839fe91dbdd3e17708bd6082f193e7693c","tid":781114,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T16:00:17.000Z","msg":"好似香港無直航，要飛台灣先然後轉機直達。聽聞無嘢玩，得陽光與海灘。記住要試下生食海芯內藏"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T17:23:43.000Z","msg":"你老母就冇嘢玩，人地海洋保育做得好過好多地方，每年又有限制遊客人數，去一去潛水睇下海洋生物乜都抵返晒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T18:25:14.000Z","msg":"我老母真係無嘢玩，你老母好玩啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd02908a33b82611fe84ee99c36b38dec3156ca3","tid":781114,"uid":123701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T01:02:55.000Z","msg":"請問唔識潛水仲有咩玩？"},{"pid":"e2e2b75168ee7f5be38330d24c1dfb0f98e683eb","tid":781114,"uid":82929,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"cd02908a33b82611fe84ee99c36b38dec3156ca3","tid":781114,"uid":123701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T01:02:55.000Z","msg":"請問唔識潛水仲有咩玩？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T01:25:55.000Z","msg":"去學潛水<br />\n唔like 潛水唔好去帛琉<br />\n仲有唔好join亞洲人（支那、台灣、泡菜人）開嘅潛店<br />\n佢地唔撚識經營，成日鳩up天氣唔好唔帶人去潛點<br />\nLunch 帶人食當地平價野味（蝙蝠、老鼠）、貓魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鬼佬團起碼會有麵包、咖啡、煙肉、蛋、芝士、火腿、沙律，鬼佬團少因爲天氣取消潛點<br />\n<br />\n如果唔鍾意落大海，剩係想陽光海灘，唔好去帛琉<br />\n去關島、澳洲仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e55bf1fc2ea051f4e8f15fdede5ab8f0c910a544","tid":781114,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2e2b75168ee7f5be38330d24c1dfb0f98e683eb","tid":781114,"uid":82929,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"cd02908a33b82611fe84ee99c36b38dec3156ca3","tid":781114,"uid":123701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T01:02:55.000Z","msg":"請問唔識潛水仲有咩玩？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T01:25:55.000Z","msg":"去學潛水<br />\n唔like 潛水唔好去帛琉<br />\n仲有唔好join亞洲人（支那、台灣、泡菜人）開嘅潛店<br />\n佢地唔撚識經營，成日鳩up天氣唔好唔帶人去潛點<br />\nLunch 帶人食當地平價野味（蝙蝠、老鼠）、貓魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鬼佬團起碼會有麵包、咖啡、煙肉、蛋、芝士、火腿、沙律，鬼佬團少因爲天氣取消潛點<br />\n<br />\n如果唔鍾意落大海，剩係想陽光海灘，唔好去帛琉<br />\n去關島、澳洲仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T01:39:09.000Z","msg":"一講潛水一陣就成班香港打手入晒嚟. <br />\n一定要香港學潛, 因為屎水夠污糟, 講嚟講去都係一個POINT. <br />\n全世界要學潛水, 就要嚟香港學, 如果唔係就唔識安全意識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"627edcf82726686a59c5e34cb6eb8495011b518a","tid":781114,"uid":66202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T02:37:02.000Z","msg":"我會預20-30K<br />\n玩都係水上活動多, 獨木舟, 無人島浮潛+bbq, 外島探險, 陽光海灘, 同海豚游水果類<br />\n<br />\n潛水係靚嘅, 可以睇到鯊魚蘇眉同埋魚群, 但係帛琉最靚嘅潛點技術要求好高, 初學者唔會帶你去, 就算你去到即刻學都無用, 如果你好多時間先去學, 如果唔係join體驗潛水會好啲<br />\n<br />\nPeleliu係二戰出名嘅大戰場, 可以去睇戰爭遺跡"},{"pid":"c1de39d009019d97103662c116de43004b02468b","tid":781114,"uid":66202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T02:39:22.000Z","msg":"以前去過水母湖好靚, 不過好似最近死左好多封左唔知有無開返, 另外有個牛奶湖可以玩火山泥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37298d4cf70d5c49643c61c55c1025f0c8b185ca","tid":781114,"uid":71323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T03:53:55.000Z","msg":"如果淨係浮潛，睇到嘅海靚唔靚？"},{"pid":"949773ee6eea44c23964a3784d552f6664bc8d89","tid":781114,"uid":21121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"37298d4cf70d5c49643c61c55c1025f0c8b185ca","tid":781114,"uid":71323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T03:53:55.000Z","msg":"如果淨係浮潛，睇到嘅海靚唔靚？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T04:04:15.000Z","msg":"好靚"},{"pid":"a0fa24248196bfa3d51008d8be7c89d2cfd38dff","tid":781114,"uid":21121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T04:06:37.000Z","msg":"個陣我係飛去台灣再JOIN 台灣旅行團玩5日4夜, 唔駛煩<br />\n團係出發之前3,4個月係香港用EMAIL 同sales 傾同俾錢<br />\n每日都係去唔同景點浮潛<br />\n唔計飛台灣個程用左1萬蚊鬆D"},{"pid":"baf932f880e87093e5fe5e9de1147e7b7049054e","tid":781114,"uid":21121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd02908a33b82611fe84ee99c36b38dec3156ca3","tid":781114,"uid":123701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T01:02:55.000Z","msg":"請問唔識潛水仲有咩玩？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T04:23:49.000Z","msg":"可以浮潛, 都好靚"},{"pid":"e5b6c410fea1712f9a08d20ac7b405098d1411a4","tid":781114,"uid":82929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e55bf1fc2ea051f4e8f15fdede5ab8f0c910a544","tid":781114,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2e2b75168ee7f5be38330d24c1dfb0f98e683eb","tid":781114,"uid":82929,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"cd02908a33b82611fe84ee99c36b38dec3156ca3","tid":781114,"uid":123701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T01:02:55.000Z","msg":"請問唔識潛水仲有咩玩？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T01:25:55.000Z","msg":"去學潛水<br />\n唔like 潛水唔好去帛琉<br />\n仲有唔好join亞洲人（支那、台灣、泡菜人）開嘅潛店<br />\n佢地唔撚識經營，成日鳩up天氣唔好唔帶人去潛點<br />\nLunch 帶人食當地平價野味（蝙蝠、老鼠）、貓魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鬼佬團起碼會有麵包、咖啡、煙肉、蛋、芝士、火腿、沙律，鬼佬團少因爲天氣取消潛點<br />\n<br />\n如果唔鍾意落大海，剩係想陽光海灘，唔好去帛琉<br />\n去關島、澳洲仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T01:39:09.000Z","msg":"一講潛水一陣就成班香港打手入晒嚟. <br />\n一定要香港學潛, 因為屎水夠污糟, 講嚟講去都係一個POINT. <br />\n全世界要學潛水, 就要嚟香港學, 如果唔係就唔識安全意識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T04:30:16.000Z","msg":"香港學潛水=學潛屎水"},{"pid":"f8038eb139491348b0e3b34f77d61068bce4ef03","tid":781114,"uid":66202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"baf932f880e87093e5fe5e9de1147e7b7049054e","tid":781114,"uid":21121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd02908a33b82611fe84ee99c36b38dec3156ca3","tid":781114,"uid":123701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T01:02:55.000Z","msg":"請問唔識潛水仲有咩玩？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T04:23:49.000Z","msg":"可以浮潛, 都好靚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T05:22:55.000Z","msg":"重有海底漫步<br />\n<br />\n另外體驗潛水有導遊係水底全程捉住你游無學過一樣玩得<br />\n<br />\n帛琉四周圍咩都無零污染, 個海靚到你係水面見到都想跳落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"353b92514d41a4951cd3c1e6bde9d02abcd6ad2d","tid":781114,"uid":66202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T05:27:56.000Z","msg":"去撚海豚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.dolphinspacific.com/top-e.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dolphinspacific.com%2Ftop-e.html&d=m4ZxF1MwPX7d0LUxAALfZ%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=4822016a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.dolphinspacific.com/top-e.html</a>"}]}